Mi d-innejmaɛ ɣuṛ-es waṭas n yemdanen ( i gellan ), acḥal ihi anagar kra n yergazen i gesɛan azal akteṛ n widak yumnen s Lmasiḥ, mi gessemfaṛaqen ɣer daxel n lebḥeṛ, mkul tutlayt ur nețwassen ara. S wakka a nemneɛ si tegzirt-nni, ur zmiren ara ad ffɣen seg wemkan-nni ajdid, ad țțuneqden zdat-es.
Daymi i glaq aț-țḍeggṛem seg ulawen-nwen ayen akk ur nzeddig ara, d wayen yellan d cceṛ deg-sen m'ara heggin iman-nsen ɣef wannect-agi, ama d sebba n ccan neɣ m'ulac aț-țcerreg ;
Ur qbilen ara ad ṭṭfen di Lmasiḥ yellan d irgazen-nsen, ad ẓren ayen i sen-yewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi. Mi d-yenna ayagi, yeǧǧa-t-id ifassen d ilmawen.
Deg ussan-nni, acḥal iberdan i d-yusan ad awḍen ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ, imdanen meṛṛa ad sɛeddin deg ubrid n Lmasiḥ, m'ara ilin di mkul amkan ;
