Yuɣ lḥal tella dinna yiwet n tqeḍɛit n yilfan kessen ; daymi i sen-d-nniɣ yiwen n wacḥal n tezmar nniḍen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, anagar ayen i d-yenna deg wawal-agi.
Llant aṭas n leṣnaf n temẓi i gellan, qqiment-ed i tent-id-yezzin akk-d țṛellaz, tekcem-iten tugdi, lameɛna llan kra wayen yellan deg-sen daɣen wid i ten-id-ițbegginen belli d yiwen ur izmir a t- ’.
