Imdanen n temdint n Babilun akk-d Sidi Ṛebbi mkul yiwen seg-sen i d-yekkan si lǧameɛ-agi iqedsen, i gețḥemmid Sidi Ṛebbi.
Imdanen-agi ad ilin d irgazen n tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen yerna ad sɛunt lḥeṛma, ad sɛunt lḥeṛma, ad lhint d yexxam-nsent iwakken iɛdawen n Sidi Ṛebbi akk-d Izimer.
Di mkul amkan n lḥekmat ț-țejmaɛt tameqqrant, tusa-d ɣer uzniqt isufa n tmes n Cciṭan ɣer wemkan iqedsen iwakken a d-yessiweḍ lexbaṛ i wid akk i t-iḍuɛen.
