Yella dinna ubuqal yeččuṛen d lxell. Dmen-d ameččim n taḍuṭ cudden-t ɣer yixef n uɣanim, s wakka ɣer wemkan iqedsen ara t-yeẓran.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n Lidya, yella leṛwaḥ n wid iwumi qqaṛen daɣen axxam tameqqrant ;
