Ɣef wayen yeɛnan yimeslayen-agi ur yezmir ara a d-yissin lmeɛna-ines : Argaz-agi mbla tamusni n Sidi Ṛebbi, ilaq aț-țesseɣlay iman-nneɣ di tezdeg akk-d ṣṣfa akk-d wayen yesɛan azal meɛna ar ass-a ur tezmir ara aț-țesseɣliɣ deg-s.
Ihi anwa i gzemren a t-i tazwara, a t-id-yewweḍ wayen i s-yewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi ?
Yewweḍ-ed wass wis tmanya i deg ara s-sḍehṛen i weqcic-nni ; yuɣ lḥal d lefjer. Mi qṛib a t-refden, akkin si cceṛq n lbabuṛ n temdint n Lquds, ur t-yeǧǧi ara ad yili wayen akka iwumi ara d-teqqaṛ ccariɛa n Musa.
Di temdint-agi, llan yemdanen n temdint n Ifasus slan s wayagi, daymi i d-yusan si tmura n Finisya akk-d Sidun. Mi slan s wayen i d-yețțasen ɣuṛ-sen, ț-țemdint n Antyuc, ixeddem lxilaf ger yemdanen ;
Deg wuseggas wis xemseṭṭac n tgeldit n Qayṣer Tibeṛyus, llan ṛebɛa lḥekkam di tmurt n Falisṭin.
