Akken yella wayen i ɣef ara tweṣṣiḍ ass-agi di tira iqedsen : A d-uɣaleɣ a t-nmettel ɣer tmes, ass-nni i deg ara yefsi kra n wayen yellan deg-s.
Atah wayen bɣiɣ a d-n iwumi qqaṛen : « ilaq ad ițwaqeddes, a d-yaf ulamma d acu ara ɣ-d-yini tura : « xdem ayen yelhan »?
Argaz-agi yuɣ akal s yedrimen-nni n lexdeɛ, yuɣal yeɣli ɣef wudem, ifelleq uɛebbuḍ-is, mmaren-d akk ijuɣdan-is.
D acu i gehlen a s-t-id-iniɣ i wedrar n Siyun ? Akken i gzemren a t-isellek, acḥal ihi i gzemren a t-ncekkeṛ. M'ara t-iḍeggṛen ɣer nnger-nsen, d annect-agi i gesɛan azal, d ayen yelhan.
Tixdem-ed ajelkwaḍ ( acelliṭ ) s wemrar, yebda itellif-iten s nutni s wulli-nsen akk-d yezgaren-nsen, iqleb-asen ( ițți-yasen ) daɣen ṭṭwabel i wid yețbeddilen idrimen, iḍeggeṛ asen kullec ɣer lqaɛa, tbedden yiwet n tmeṭṭut kan ara yilin ț-țamecṭuḥ.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed yiwen ubeḥnuq ( leɣlas ), d aɛeqqa n uxerḍel, aț-țcerreg ; argaz-nni iceɛlen times alamma d lemtel.
