Ccariɛa n tejmaɛt n temdint n Lquds, yewwi-t zzhu-nsen ɣer temdint n Lquds azal n tlata uṛebɛin iseggasen. Wid akk i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda armi d ass n lḥisab, armi d ass n lḥisab i d-ițbegginen aṭas n tejmaɛt i deg uran lumuṛat n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin n tikli-ines armi ț-țigzirt n Qubṛus, lexbaṛ n lxiṛ yeɛnan leɛyubat n leṛwaḥ n wid n lemwaji ț-țemdint n Antyuc.
