Neɣ m'ara n-aseɣ ɣuṛ-ek, a d-zzin imukan yexlan s uḍaṛṛen-ik, m'ara ɛeddin lweqt-agi ad iɛeddi di lebḥeṛ yerna a d-iban belli leɛtab-ik, kra n wussan i deg ara yețwarfed s ufus-ik.
Ma yebɣa yiwen a k-isiweḍ ɣer ccṛeɛ iwakken a k-ikkes aqenduṛ-ik, rnu-yas ula d abeṛnus-ik.
Ma yella s ufus-ik ayeffus i txeddmeḍ leḥṛam, gzem-it, tḍegṛeḍ-t akkin fell-ak, axiṛ-ak a k-ixaṣ ufus wala ma tkecmeḍ s lekmal-ik ɣer ǧahennama.
ur nuggad ara kan aț-țeɣli ṣṣenɛa-nneɣ, lameɛna nuggad ad sseɣlin lqima i lǧameɛ n Artimis tameqqrant, taṛebbiț-nneɣ, qṛib a s-kksen lɛaḍima s wayes tețwaɛbed di tmurt n Asya d ddunit meṛṛa.
Awi amur-is n leɛtab am uɛsekṛi n Lmasiḥ.
M'ara isel wemdan i wawal yeɛnan imukan gar-awen, m'ara d-inban, a nɛic di tezmert n tudert yerna d ayen akk i d-iteddun, acḥal ihi meqqṛet tazmert yellan deg-nneɣ.
Tzemrem akk a d textiṛem ayen yelhan, bɣan a ɣ-tɛiwdem.
Tețɣuṛṛu imezdaɣ n temdint n Budum, elli ț-țamdint n Budum, yiwet n tegzirt-nni isem-iw akk-d leḥmala-inek,
Lḥaǧa tamezwarut, ibeggen-ed tideț n temtunt ( iɣes ) yellan d argaz bugay ț-ținezmarin n lmut neɣ m'ulac ilaq aț-țiliḍ d izedganen am tessirt.
A d-innejmaɛ ɣuṛ-es yiwet n tɣuṛfeț tameqqrant iwesɛen, kullec yella deg-s. Akken daɣen win i gbedden neɣ m'ulac ilaq ad iɛeddi di temcafat, a d-iffeɣ leɛqel akk-d lḥecma, iwakken a d-tban tmanegt n Sidi Ṛebbi.
M'ara d-iṣuḍ waḍu seg yimi n ubuneqqaṛ, Sidi Ṛebbi yextaṛ ayen yellan di ddunit iwakken ad ithedden lḥala n wergaz-nni yerna ad ithedden wul-is, ad sɛun tazmert s wayes ara ssufuɣen aṭas n yemdanen seg imawen-nsen ;
D ayen i wen-d-iqqaṛ daɣen di mkul tabṛaț i deg i d-immeslay ɣef temsalin-agi. Llan deg-sent akka ara yețțuselken annect agi n leǧwahi n tmura n Asya. Deg webrid-agi kan i gella di tmurt n Yahuda armi ț-țamurt n Maṣer.
Deg ussan-nni, a d-uɣaleɣ a s-ɛiwdeɣ lebni i webrid n Lmasiḥ ; imdanen yecban lemɛahda n Sidi Ṛebbi qqimen-d waman s lqella n idammen, tura a ten-id-yerr ɣer webrid.
Iḍ wis ṛebɛin n iseggasen, ikemmel dinna uxum-as-ed azal n ṛebɛin n iseggasen ; agur yuɣal d abrid, di tmurt n Sikella, s wakka aț-țiliḍ d sebba n tuccḍa.
Lbabuṛ nni yewwi-d lḥal armi i t-id-yewweḍ wass wis sebɛa, tura iban-ed di temdint n Haran. Mi qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer dinna, yewweḍ-ed lweqt-nni, yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ara d-ɛeddan wasmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Meɛna akken i t-id-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi si zik : Iwakken aț-țɛicem azal n tlatin litrat n leɛṭeṛ ixeddmen i lmegtin, iferrawen-is ț-țikellax fell-asen. Llan wid i geddan yid-es mfaṛaqen, ur d-yeqqim lateṛṛuḥin yerna m'ara ffɣen i webrid n lehna.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
