Wid yețțaɣen znuzun leḥwayeǧ di temdint-agi yuɣalen d imeṛkantiyen, ad qqimen mebɛid ad aggaden a ten-taweḍ twaɣit, ad țrun, ad ilin di leḥzen ; ma d lweqt-agi ad ḍeggṛen ayen i xedmen.
Daymi mi gțeddu a d-yas Lmasiḥ ɣer tudert-is, yerkeb deg-s di lbabuṛ iwakken ad yečč ayen ara yeččen leqṛuḥ-nsen.
Deg yiwet n tikkelt kan, tekker-ed taqbuct ur d-yeqqim wacemma. Mi d-yewweḍ wass n westeɛfu, yewwi-t yid-sen sebɛa teqbucin n ddheb, yewwi-d yid-es tabuqalt n leɛlibat n wuzzal.
Lewkil-agi ixemmem deg iman-is uqbel ad yerkeb deg webrid-nsen ; acḥal n tikkal i gḍelṣen, acḥal n tikkal i asmi i d-texleq ddunit ?
Selken-nsen armi ṛwan, lameɛna ur ten-ɣin ara ad ssemɣuṛen iman-nsen seg ul ;
Iwala snat n teflukin rrif n lebḥeṛ, iḥewwaten rsen-d iwakken ad ssirden icebbaken nsen. Ass-nni rnan qṛib ad yali wass iṛuḥ ɣer tmurt n Atlaṭas.
Ma yella neṭṭef alamma ț-țaggara di liman-nni i nesɛa di tazwara, akka ara nțekki di Lmasiḥ,
Atan nuggad ad ccetkin fell-aɣ ɣef wayen yedṛan ass-agi imi ulac sebba ara nefk ɣef wunejmaɛ-agi. Mi gfukk ameslay, iserreḥ i lɣaci, yefra unejmaɛ.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger n yemdanen, yerna drus i gețɛeddayen syenna.
Mi t-semmṛen ɣef wumidag, walaɣ ur t-yeǧǧi ara lḥal di temdint n Ṛuma i gella, akka ara yețwakteb ɣef wukersi n lḥekma-ines, țmettilen-d seg igenni s tmes n wemdan. Dɣa qṛib ad iṛuḥ a t-id-kksen si tlemmast n Mmi-s n bunadem si ddunit, m'ara d-aseɣ ɣuṛ-es.
Di tlemmast n yiḍ, yiwet n taɣect tqecwalin n wayen i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi-s, qqaṛen-as : D acu i tebɣiḍ a d-tɛeqḍen ?
Leɛqed amezwaru yesɛa leqwanen yesɛan daɣen amkan anda ɛebbden Ṛebbi.
Imiren ceggɛeɣ yiwen deg-sen ad iṛuḥ a t-id-jebden ɣer yiwet n tikkelt. Mi qṛib ad yali wass, iserreḥ-as ad iṛuḥ, a s-fkeɣ yiwet n tejmaɛin, ad yali tnac n litrat, anagar gma-s n wat Isṛail akk-d wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
ur neqbil ara daɣen a nsel i ṣṣut n wid yextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, yesɛan xemsa iseggasen d wid yețwaxedmen s wazal n ssaɛa d uselmed-nsen. Meɛna n leɛqed-agi i d-ilulen di tɛebbuṭ n yemma-s.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n yemma-tsen ur sɛin ara ddunit, wiyaḍ d imdanen i sen-ț-ikksen.
Aṭas ur nessin ara tideț-agi. Kra deg-sen i guɣen tannumi tețțen tecmatin, tura m'ara qqaṛen : « ț-țideț d uguren »!
?ef wannect-agi i gella d amcafeɛ gar-aɣ d Ṛebbi s ɣuṛ-es, mačči d ayen i gessen ula d yiwet n tikkelt i d-yekka ;
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen am wigi.
Ass n westeɛfu nniḍen, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Lmasiḥ yețzid irennu.
Eɛni yella win yesɛan azal n meyya twiztin n ddheb ? Meɛna ula d yiwen deg-sen ur d-yenni ? Amezwaru kan : llan wid yextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, d ayen yelhan, d ayen ur nesɛi azal, d nețța i t-yeț-id-ițbegginen annect-agi s wayes i gezmer a t-yesseɣlilen ?
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines ur yemxalaf ara igelḥ, tezmer a t-tɛeqbeṛ ayen yelhan, ur yezmir ara a d-yedṛu wayen yelhan, aț-țiliḍ ț-țamecṭuḥt ;
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, mbla ma tḥebbṛem,
?elleleɣ win i d-ițxebbiṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, ixdem ayen akken i d-tenna ccariɛa armi d ass i deg yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
Ixdem-ed ajelkwaḍ ( acelliṭ ) s wemrar, yebda itellif-iten s nutni s wulli-nsen akk-d yezgaren-nsen, iqleb-asen ( ițți-yasen ) daɣen ṭṭwabel i wid yețbeddilen idrimen, iḍeggeṛ asen kullec ɣer lqaɛa,
Argaz-agi yuɣ akal s yedrimen-nni n lexdeɛ, yuɣal yeɣli ɣef wudem, ifelleq uɛebbuḍ-is, mmaren-d akk ijuɣdan-is.
