Meɛna ma yella yefka-d isennanen d ubuneqqaṛ, d akal ur nesɛi azal, ad ițwanɛel yerna qṛib a s-ceɛlen times.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg wayen akk i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi. M'ara isel i wayen i d-yețțaken tudert n ṣṣeḥ, s ṣṣifa n wemdan akk-d umsellek am akken xeddmen i nnger-nsen.
ț-țideț, lumuṛat-agi sselmaden leɛbada, annuz akk-d uɛețțeb n lǧețțat nneɣ, țbanen-d amakken d ayen yelhan, lameɛna d ayen ur nezmir ad iɛawen bunadem ad iṭṭef iman-is.
Atah wayen i d-nniɣ d wayen iwumi yezmer wemdan. Ihi anwa i d-ițasenn i d-ikkan seg yimi-s, d ayen i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, i t-yeṭṭfen deg-s.
Aṭas n yemdanen i ten-iwalan mi ṛuḥen, ḍeggṛet di ț-țamdint iwakken ad ṛuḥen ɣer yexxamen-nsen, ad kecmen wid yelhan, ad ɛiwnen wiyaḍ, ad rren awal i Sidi Ṛebbi di mkul amkan anda yella tuben.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif agi, țɛebbiden-t yemdanen iwakken a kkun-tawren s tyunanit. Win i d-iqeṛṛeb ɣuṛ-es, ixeddmen anagar ticmatin iferrawen-nsen.
?ef wayen yeɛnan tamusni n Sidi Ṛebbi, acḥal aya segmi yeṭṭfen deg uselmed-agi. Akken daɣen ma yella wamek, acḥal i t-yewwet s yiwen n lemtel iwumi qqaṛen « Akken i t-isellek si zik s ufella-agi, deg unezṛuf ».
Țemyawit wway gar-asen iwakken ad deɛɛun ɣer Sidi Ṛebbi nutni. Akken daɣen wid akk yețnejmaɛen s lemwaji ad slen i wawal-is, s tdukli-nsen a d-inin :
Acḥal n wussan ur d-iban yiṭij ur d-banen itran, lebḥeṛ mazal-it yerwi, ur numin ara a nțwasellek.
Amek armi tḥessem i wid iwumi semman lmuṣiba issengaren i yi-len ? Acuɣeṛ i tet lqima ? Eɛni ur nețɛeddi ara akk di ccṛeɛ ? Eɛni ur nefhim ara akk-d wiyaḍ ?
Llan gar-aneɣ yemdanen i d yusan si tmurt n Bartas, si tmurt n Midyas, si tmurt n Ilam, kra nniḍen si tmurt n Mizubuṭamya, si tmurt n Yahuda akk-d tmurt n Kafadusya, wiyaḍ si tmurt n Tqenṭert, wiyaḍ si tmurt n Asya,
للأسف, m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-aneɣ, a d-yaweḍ lqebṭan n lɛeskeṛ s lǧehd, axaṭer ur yezmir ara a t-yeṛṛeq kra n wussan.
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger, ma d win ara yeṭṭfen anagar ayen yelhan, ur ixeddmen cceṛ, ilaq aț-țeṭṭfeḍ deg webrid n leslak.
M'ara d-yali yiṭij s leḥmu-ines yesseṛɣayen, imɣi ad iqqaṛ, ajeǧǧig-is ad iɣli, ccbaḥa-ines a s-tṛuḥ. Akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti , ad iṛuḥ a d-yeǧǧ deffir-es wayen akk yesɛa.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : snat n tilawin-agi țusemmant d sin leɛqud : yiwen n leɛqed d win n wedrar n Sinay i d-ițaǧǧan aklan, yeɛni : d Haǧiṛa.
Lxelq amezwaru ițemcabi ɣer yizem, lxelq wi sin yecba agenduz, leṛwaḥ n wid yeččan akteṛ-nsen a ten-ɛiwnen. Meɛna tzemmur, tekcem-iten lxelɛa ț-țameqqrant !
Win i d-yețțaken i ufellaḥ zzerriɛa akk-d weɣṛum ara yečč , a wen-d-yefk ula i kunwi s lketṛa yerna ad issefti lbaṛakat n wayen tețseddiqem .
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit wazal n tlata n twaɣyin akk-d tid n lmalayekkat-nni i sen-d-ifka Sidna Ɛisa.
Akken daɣen ula d iles ; ɣas mecṭuḥ deg yiman-is, yețzuxxu s lecɣal imeqqranen. Walit times tamecṭuḥt i gzemren aț-țesseṛɣ tiẓgi tameqqrant.
Mbeɛd ayagi, walaɣ izumal n lɣaci, yenna : Yiwen wergaz yeẓẓaden, isem-is Utikus, axaṭer d axalaf seg ugeffur ( i d-ikkan ).
Lqebṭan-nni i walan belli ayen yedṛan yedṛan yedṛan yid-sen. Llan wid i gzedɣen di lqaɛa, tewwet lḥemlayen-nni i gzemren a t-jebder ?
Argaz-agi הגיוני ț-țideț, yenna-d : Acuɣeṛ i tuggadem ? D annect-agi i d-ikkan ɣer ddunit ?
Lemfaṣel n wasif n Urdun, iččuṛ ț-țama n Lmasiḥ ț-țemdint n ddunit. Llan deg-sen snat ccetla n ddunit, aṭas n yemdanen i d-izzinen ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ.
