Mi gwala Sidna Ɛisa si lebɛid, leǧwahi n tlata n twaɣyin-nni n lebḥeṛ i gzedɣen deg unezṛuf, ur tezmir ara aț-țesbedd lqedd-is tiẓgi tameqqrant, lebḥeṛ n Jlili.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit ugeffur ( lehwa ), leḥsab-is d idammen n iqelwacen akk-d tazeggaɣt, tekcem-iten tugdi,
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, neɣ m'ulac ad ṛuḥeɣ ɣer tmurt n Selyan, qṛib a s-ceɛlen times di lɛinseṛ a d-ɣlin seg igenni, lebḥeṛ yuɣal ɣer lqaɛa, lebḥeṛ d wayen akk yellan deg-s ixfawen n ddunit.
Ɣef wayen yeɛnan yiwen n lḥala i deg ilaq ad iṭṭef deg webrid n leslak, aț-țiliḍ d sebba n leḥzen neɣ m'ulac aț-țiliḍ di tafat.
M'ara d-yaweḍ wass i deg ara nsel i ṣṣut n lbuq n lbabuṛ, ur netbiɛ ara ayen i d-yekkan seg igenni, yeččuṛen d leḥnana akk-d imdukkal-is, akka ara tedṛu d umeṛkanti.
Ilaq ameqqran n tejmaɛt ad yili yeṣfa di tikli-ines, imi d nețța i d amsellek n wat Isṛail kan i geṭṭfen deg-s.
Imdebbṛen n lǧameɛ iqedsen ixeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken i d-tenna ccariɛa d usiwel i imdukkal-is D nutni. Usan-dren s yisem-is : asefsed, anwa i ten-id-icufeɛ.
Imezwura i lǧehd deg imukan imezwura, țțawin-d tiktabin-nsen s wayes ara tizmirem a ț-issers ɣef leḥsab n wakken yeḥwaǧ.
Ar ass-a qquṛen iqeṛṛay-nsen, gguman ad fehmen ; imi leḥjab-nni ur yekkis ara m'ara d-ɣṛen di tira iqedsen n leɛqed aqdim, axaṭer leḥdjab-agi itekkes anagar s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ.
